# UI/UX Guidelines

## Design System

1. Use shadcn/ui components as the foundation
2. Implement consistent spacing using Tailwind's scale
3. Follow the established color palette
4. Maintain consistent typography hierarchy

## Component Design

1. Use Lucide React icons for consistency
2. Implement proper loading states
3. Handle error states gracefully
4. Add hover and focus states for interactive elements
5. Ensure proper contrast ratios for accessibility

## Responsive Design

1. Design mobile-first
2. Use Tailwind's breakpoint system
3. Ensure touch targets are appropriately sized
4. Test layouts across different screen sizes

## Accessibility

1. Use semantic HTML elements
2. Implement proper ARIA labels
3. Ensure keyboard navigation works
4. Maintain sufficient color contrast
5. Support screen readers

## Performance

1. Optimize images using Next.js Image component
2. Implement proper loading strategies
3. Use code splitting where appropriate
4. Minimize bundle size
5. Follow Core Web Vitals guidelines
